{"tid":1949022,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 點解冰島可以 香港唔得？","createTime":"2020-03-29T11:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T03:17:12.000Z","uid":7439,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a829b5f1cc16ec8376f3ae6f1f53cefa1735ce","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19）在全球肆虐，而且病毒在持續變種，令它變得更難為醫學界與科學家所了解。冰島媒體3月24日報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">一名冰島病人體內同時存有兩種武漢肺炎病毒，其中一個為原始病毒的變異種，可能是全球首次出現「雙重感染者」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冰島雜誌《Reykjav&iacute;k Grapevine》報道，冰島基因公司德科德（deCODE）針對當地確診患者進行研究，發現40種新冠病毒變種。<br />\n<br />\n公司同時發現其中一名患者體內，出現不尋常的雙重感染。公司行政總裁斯特凡松（Kari Stefansson）23日指出，患者出現2種新冠肺炎病毒，已變異的病毒較原先病毒更具傳染力及致命力，因為「雙重感染者」身上只發現第2種病株。<br />\n<br />\n若情況屬實，代表病毒會隨時間推移突變，並變得更具傳染性。不過斯特凡松表示，目前尚無法證實這一點，不排除只是巧合。但無論如何，這都是全球首宗「雙重感染者」。<br />\n<br />\n公司又指出，分析顯示冰島的病毒來源相當廣泛，主要來自意大利、奧地利及英國等地，其中一場在英國舉行的足球比賽，據指造成7名冰島人染疫。"},{"pid":"8257decd40d95081826d549f4cc643f70d7c82d7","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冰島至今確診963宗新冠肺炎個案、2宗死亡個案。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冰島本身都唔係強隊<br />\n點解冰島可以 香港唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5297232e6ab00acd056866064167c58688a815","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"Kari Stefansson兼職做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81c18496d88f3180f771b50cedd5aef8c991042","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地天生身體質素都贏成截<br />\n</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2ca92eb581380da377dce333f123dcfa3d090d","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬點同維京人比</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>人地除左番工仲有生活</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89805f5b0e214b8b6adbdc4dd759d9e887539819","tid":1949022,"uid":2607,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:14:31.000Z","msg":"香港有能力驗都唔比公佈啦"},{"pid":"56c44d33c44068896a8116659ba1e4054e5a0979","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地係戰鬥民族<br />\n天生對抗北極嚴寒<br />\n香港呢 十幾度都著羽絨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635c5b66d8d8fbd9e3df02dc94025d979f1d1ef0","tid":1949022,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"樓主勁小氣。。"},{"pid":"124ffad7cedd5af1c62f079c4a73cf4602261c9b","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"冰島衛生部<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.covid.is/tolulegar-upplysingar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.covid.is%2Ftolulegar-upplysingar&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=38e8c2b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.covid.is/tolulegar-upplysingar</a><br />\n邊格係死亡人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3875f5132ea76097ce8ddeea9a1fe3583c9f6554","tid":1949022,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>K&aacute;ri 又指，目前冰島確診個案主要來自意大利、奧地利和英國，其中一場在英國進行的足球比賽更導致7名冰島人受感染。<br />\n可是他們並未公布是哪一場比賽和涉及哪些球隊。</blockquote><br />\n人地凝聚力強到痴線<br />\n我地唔抵得自己友贏都強到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ae56847ccfe20a14116c0211543546bd475125","tid":1949022,"uid":11254,"lik